data.description: Spacious and comfortable, this four bedroom, two bath home offers ample room for a growing family. The home offers great gathering space with a living room and separate family room. Not to mention a newer back deck with a fenced in back yard. Updates include new master shower, vanity and flooring. Newer vanity in hall bath and updated shower. New gutters, soffits and facia. Don't miss out!
